               2. Tim. 1. 4. 5. 
               he was aſſured did dwell in him alſo: And here the Apoſtle willeth the Corintians, to try themſelves if they bee in the faith, and againe to the Coloſſians, If ye continue grounded and stabliſhed in the faith, &amp; 
                  Col. 1. 23. againe, as ye haue received Chriſt Ieſus the Lord walk in him, rooted 
               
                  Ibidem. 2, 6, 7. 
